+
+    // Mid-range purity
+    int ptm_enable;     // The Mid Purity module adjusts mid-range purity of midtones and highlights. Without this module enabled, it is likely that midtones will not appear colorful enough, and highlights will appear too colorful resulting in chaulky pasty looking images especially in yellows and cyans.
